      "id": "ROlb",
      "code_hash": "dfae224d232db2cb417bd9d33455ca95",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><hr />\n<h2 id=\"how-it-works\">How It Works</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">This widget combines:</span>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://anywidget.dev/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">anywidget</a></strong> - Portable widget framework</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://wavesurfer.xyz/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">wavesurfer.js</a></strong> - Audio visualization (loaded from CDN)</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://marimo.io/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">marimo</a></strong> - Reactive Python notebooks</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"key-features\">Key Features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Bidirectional sync</strong>: Python \u2194 JavaScript state automatically synchronized via traitlets</li>\n<li><strong>Multi-pitch audio</strong>: Generated sample uses 3 musical notes (A4, C5, E5) forming A major chord</li>\n<li><strong>File upload support</strong>: Upload your own audio files (MP3, WAV, OGG, M4A)</li>\n<li><strong>Self-contained</strong>: Works immediately - no build step, no external dependencies</li>\n<li><strong>Interactive</strong>: Drag regions, click table rows, play audio - everything updates reactively</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"use-cases\">Use Cases</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Audio transcription and annotation</li>\n<li>Podcast chapter marking</li>\n<li>Music analysis (verse/chorus/bridge)</li>\n<li>Language learning with sentence-level audio</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Resources</strong>:\n<a href=\"https://wavesurfer.xyz/docs/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">wavesurfer.js docs</a> \u2022\n<a href=\"https://anywidget.dev/en/getting-started/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">anywidget guide</a> \u2022\n<a href=\"https://marimo.io/gallery\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">marimo gallery</a></span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    }
  ]
